(NULL, 'Which dynasty ruled Odisha during the construction of the Konark Sun Temple?', 'Eastern Ganga Dynasty', 'Bhoi Dynasty', 'Keshari Dynasty', 'Somavamsi Dynasty', 'A', 1, 'History', 'medium', '["Eastern Ganga Dynasty", "Konark", "History", "Dynasties"]'::jsonb, 'The Eastern Ganga Dynasty, under King Narasimhadeva I, ruled Odisha during the 13th century when the Konark Sun Temple was built.'),
(NULL, 'The famous Kalinga War was fought in 261 BCE. Which modern city is closest to the battlefield?', 'Bhubaneswar', 'Cuttack', 'Puri', 'Berhampur', 'A', 1, 'History', 'medium', '["Kalinga War", "Ashoka", "Bhubaneswar", "History"]'::jsonb, 'The Kalinga War was fought near modern-day Bhubaneswar. The Dhauli hills, where Ashoka''s rock edicts are located, are near the battlefield.'),
