(NULL, 'Which famous battle in 1803 led to the British annexation of Odisha?', 'Battle of Plassey', 'Battle of Buxar', 'Battle of Puri', 'Battle of Cuttack', 'C', 1, 'History', 'hard', '["British Rule", "History", "Battle of Puri", "1803"]'::jsonb, 'The Battle of Puri in 1803, where the British defeated the Marathas, led to the British annexation of Odisha and the end of Maratha rule.'),

